{
  "stem": "26142.12",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I have to mention that my brother [NON-ENGLISH] wife and her little baby was home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But they were afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were afraid to-- to communicate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he was back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he didn't see his baby for another year.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, he didn't see her till sometime in November or December of 1942.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 11 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I took chances in 19-- when my brother [NON-ENGLISH] was already in Satu Mare, I took chances from Debrecen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a three hour train ride.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I took the chance twice to take the train, and go down and meet him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the only-- the only real help that we gave him-- being together all this time didn't give him any help at all.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe he felt a little bit more secure.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The only real help that we gave him was that we crossed first.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were able to let our parents know where he is.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they were able to send-- otherwise, you can't send in a place somebody you don't know where.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That That was the real help that we gave him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And a little later, I think in November, he left-- he left-- he meaning [NON-ENGLISH], left Satu Mare.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he went to a city called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "For what reason he went there, I think-- I think he managed to get some kind of a job over there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] This dragged on-- I-- I have to-- I have to-- I think I'm going to skip this here, because it's taking too long.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "With all this time, my parents were spending a fortune to legalize-- to get us the Hungarian citizenship.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he had a lawyer in Budapest, which cost a fortune.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we finally did get this citizenship, because they couldn't deny it.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
